# Design Standards & Best Practices

## Typography
- **Headings (h1, h2)**: Use 'Playfair Display' serif font with font-weight: 300 (light)
- **Body text**: Use 'Montserrat' sans-serif font with font-weight: 300 (light)
- **Font sizes**:
  - h1: 2em
  - h2: 1.3em
  - Body: default (1em)
  - Small text: 0.9em
- **Line height**: 1.6 for body text, 1.7 for descriptions
- **Color hierarchy**:
  - Primary text: #333
  - Secondary text: #666
  - Tertiary text: #777

## Border Radius / Corner Rounding
- **Small elements** (skill tags, icons): 20px (border-radius: 20px)
- **Medium elements** (cards, containers): 10px (border-radius: 10px)
- **Large elements**: Use sparingly, typically 10px max

## Spacing
- **Section spacing**: 25px margin-bottom
- **Item spacing**: 30px margin-bottom for experience items, 25px for education items
- **Padding**: 40px for main container (20px on mobile)
- **Gap spacing**: 15px for contact info, 8px for skill tags, 10px for flex gaps

## Colors
- **Background**: #fff (white)
- **Text primary**: #333
- **Text secondary**: #666
- **Text tertiary**: #777
- **Borders**: rgba(0,0,0,0.05) for subtle dividers, rgba(0,0,0,0.1) for grid lines
- **Skill tags**: rgba(0,0,0,0.05) background

## Glassmorphism
- **Background**: rgba(255,255,255,0.3)
- **Backdrop filter**: blur(10px)
- **Border**: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5)
- **Shadow**: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)

## Icons
- **Size**: 14x14px for contact icons
- **Style**: Fill-based SVG icons using currentColor
- **Spacing**: 6px margin-right from icon to text

## Layout
- **Max width**: 800px for content container
- **Centering**: Use flexbox with align-items: center and justify-content: center
- **Responsive breakpoint**: 768px

## Borders & Dividers
- **Item dividers**: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05)
- **Grid lines**: 2px dashed rgba(0,0,0,0.1)
- **Last child**: Remove border-bottom from last items

## Font Weights
- **Headings**: 300 (light)
- **Titles**: 600 (semi-bold)
- **Body**: 300 (light)
- **Bold text**: 600 (semi-bold)

## Best Practices
- Use semantic HTML elements
- Maintain consistent spacing rhythm
- Keep design minimal and clean
- Use rgba for transparency effects
- Ensure proper contrast for accessibility
- Use flexbox for layouts
- Add responsive design considerations at 768px breakpoint
